        <article class="Section__block-article Section__block-article_right">
            <h3 class="Section__block-article_caption">Wildlife of Antarctica</h3>
            <p class="Section__block-article_description">The most abundant and best known animals from the southern continent. Penguins, whales seals, albatrosses, other seabirds and a range of invertebrates you may have not heard of such as krill which form the basis of the Antarctic food web. </p>
        </article>
